import{_ as e,o,c as t,b as c}from"./app-de7a4551.js";const s={},a=c('<h1 id="computers" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#computers" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Computers</h1><p>Computers are a <code>vital</code> part of modern life. They have <code>revolutionized</code> the way we work, communicate, and <code>access</code> information.</p><details class="custom-container details"><summary>translation</summary><p><strong>sentence:</strong></p><p>计算机是现代生活的重要组成部分。它们改变了我们工作、交流和获取信息的方式。</p><p><strong>words:</strong></p><p>vital<br><code>美: [ˈvaɪt(ə)l] 英: [&#39;vaɪt(ə)l]</code></p><blockquote><p>adj. 必不可少的；对…极重要的；生命的；维持生命所必需的</p></blockquote><p>revolutionize<br><code>美: [ˌrevəˈluʃ(ə)nˌaɪz] 英: [ˌrevəˈluːʃəˌnaɪz]</code></p><blockquote><p>v. 革新；使革命化；引起革命；鼓吹革命思想</p></blockquote><p>access<br><code>美: [ˈækˌses] 英: [ˈækses]</code></p><blockquote><p>v. 进入；〈正式〉到达；【IT】获得或储存(电脑文件)<br> n. 通道；入口；机会；权力</p></blockquote></details><p>One of the most important functions of computers is processing data. This can include tasks such as word processing, <code>spreadsheet</code> editing, and <code>graphic</code> design. With the help of powerful <code>processors</code> and high-<code>performance</code> software, computers can handle large amounts of data quickly and <code>efficiently</code>.</p><details class="custom-container details"><summary>translation</summary><p><strong>sentence:</strong></p><p>计算机最重要的功能之一是处理数据。这可以包括诸如文字处理、电子表格编辑和图形设计等任务。在强大的处理器和高性能软件的帮助下，计算机可以快速而高效地处理大量数据。</p><p><strong>words:</strong></p><p>spreadsheet<br><code>美: [ˈspredˌʃɪt] 英: [ˈspredˌʃiːt]</code></p><blockquote><p>n. 电子表格</p></blockquote><p>graphic<br><code>美: [ˈɡræfɪk] 英: [&#39;ɡræfɪk]</code></p><blockquote><p>n. 图形<br> 　adj. 绘画的；书画的；图样的；图案的</p></blockquote><p>processor<br><code>美: [ˈprɑˌsesər] 英: [ˈprəʊˌsesə(r)]</code></p><blockquote><p>n. (数据等的)分理者；【自】信息处理机；〈美〉农产品加工者</p></blockquote><p>performance<br><code>美: [pəˈfɔrməns] 英: [pə(r)ˈfɔː(r)məns]</code></p><blockquote><p>n. 性能；表现；业绩；表演</p></blockquote><p>efficiently<br><code>英: [ɪ&#39;fɪʃ(ə)ntli]</code></p><blockquote><p>adv. 有效；效率；井井有条地；干练</p></blockquote></details><p>Another important <code>aspect</code> of computers is their ability to connect people from all over the world. Through the internet, we can communicate with others in real-time, no matter where they are located. This has transformed the way we do business, learn, and <code>socialize</code>.</p><details class="custom-container details"><summary>translation</summary><p><strong>sentence:</strong></p><p>计算机的另一个重要方面是它们能够连接来自世界各地的人们。通过互联网，我们可以实时与他人沟通，无论他们身在何处。这已经改变了我们做生意、学习和社交的方式。</p><p><strong>words:</strong></p><p>aspect<br><code>美: [ˈæspekt] 英: [&#39;æspekt]</code></p><blockquote><p>n. 方面；层面；外观；方位</p></blockquote><p>socialize<br><code>美: [ˈsoʊʃ(ə)lˌaɪz] 英: [ˈsəʊʃəlaɪz]</code></p><blockquote><p>v. 交际；使适应社会；使社会主义化；按社会主义原则行事</p></blockquote></details><p>Computers have also had a <code>significant</code> <code>impact</code> on education. With online learning platforms and educational software, students can access educational resources from anywhere at any time. This has made education more <code>accessible</code> and convenient for people of all ages and backgrounds.</p><details class="custom-container details"><summary>translation</summary><p><strong>sentence:</strong></p><p>计算机对教育也产生了重大影响。通过在线学习平台和教育软件，学生可以从任何地方随时访问教育资源。这使得教育对于各个年龄和背景的人来说更加易于获得和方便。</p><p><strong>words:</strong></p><p>significant<br><code>美: [sɪɡˈnɪfɪkənt] 英: [sɪɡ&#39;nɪfɪkənt]</code></p><blockquote><p>adj. 有重大意义的；显著的；有某种意义的；别有含义的</p></blockquote><p>impact<br><code>美: [ɪmˈpækt] 英: [ɪm&#39;pækt]</code></p><blockquote><p>v. 冲击；撞击；有作用<br> n. 撞击；冲击力；冲撞；巨大影响</p></blockquote><p>accessible<br><code>美: [əkˈsesəb(ə)l] 英: [ək&#39;sesəb(ə)l]</code></p><blockquote><p>adj. 可到达的；可接近的；可进入的；可使用的</p></blockquote></details><p>Overall, computers have become an <code>essential</code> tool in our daily lives. Whether we are working, communicating, learning, or simply browsing the internet, computers play a <code>critical</code> role in making these activities possible. As technology continues to advance, it is exciting to think about the new ways that computers will continue to <code>shape</code> our world.</p><details class="custom-container details"><summary>translation</summary><p><strong>sentence:</strong></p><p>总的来说，计算机已经成为我们日常生活中必不可少的工具。无论我们是工作、交流、学习还是只是浏览互联网，计算机都在使这些活动成为可能的关键作用。随着技术的不断进步，我们很兴奋地想象计算机将继续以新的方式塑造我们的世界。</p><p><strong>words:</strong></p><p>essential<br><code>美: [ɪˈsenʃ(ə)l] 英: [ɪ&#39;senʃ(ə)l]</code></p><blockquote><p>n. 要点；要素；实质；必需品<br> adj. 完全必要的；必不可少的；极其重要的；本质的</p></blockquote><p>critical<br><code>美: [ˈkrɪtɪk(ə)l] 英: [&#39;krɪtɪk(ə)l]</code></p><blockquote><p>adj. 批评的；批判性的；挑剔的；极重要的</p></blockquote><p>shape<br><code>美: [ʃeɪp] 英: [ʃeɪp]</code></p><blockquote><p>n. 形状；外形；状况；样子<br> v. 塑造；使成为…形状（或样子）；决定…的形成；影响…的发展<br> abbr. (=Supreme Headquarters； Allied Powers in Europe)(北大西洋公约组织的)欧洲盟军最高司令部</p></blockquote></details>',11),r=[a];function n(p,d){return o(),t("div",null,r)}const l=e(s,[["render",n],["__file","31-computer.html.vue"]]);export{l as default};
